Class MapController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.MapController

  • public class MapController
extends java.lang.Object
    Map Controller to generate a random paparazzi maps for the defined data set. Controller is implemented in a Singleton pattern.

      • generateMap

        public PaparazziMap generateMap(MapDataSets dataSet)
        Generates new random paparazzi map and sets map cells. After random creation, the map is checked with Dijkstra if its possible to solve. are: Normal Cell, Start Cell, End Cell, Wall Cell, Camera Cell, Camera Radius Cell, Pond Cell.
        Parameters:
        dataSet - the Map Data Set that should be created
        Returns:
        the generated paparazzi map to solve
        See Also:
        PaparazziMap
